{"tid":2334811,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"一名城巴車長確診　上周四及周五曾駕駛307A及5X","createTime":"2020-12-21T11:31:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T11:31:40.000Z","uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f9c1db206bbfdd547624bc4e2c1549630fb1fee0","tid":2334811,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T11:31:40.000Z","msg":"一名城巴車長確診新型肺炎。城巴表示，確診車長曾於上周四及周五，分別駕駛307A及5X路線。<br />\n<br />\n確診車長曾駕駛於早上7時05分開出，由大埔前往上環的307A，以及上午9時至中午1時、來往堅尼地城與銅鑼灣的5X路線，涉及4輛巴士，車身編號分別為8399、8451、6368及6347。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1566478-20201221.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1566478-20201221.htm&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzHs01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=576b6fac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1566478-20201221.htm&h=a7a2515f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1566478-20201221.htm</a>"}]}